org.apache.commons.io.function

Class Uncheck

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.io.function.Uncheck

  • public final class Uncheck
extends java.lang.Object
    Unchecks calls by throwing UncheckedIOException instead of IOException.
    Since:
    2.12.0
